243 倍率</p>\n<p>包月额度最多相当于 0.1755 倍率</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779948716, "replies": 64, "id": 1216160}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/884d/7996/1160_large.png?m=1771515639", "name": "vibecoding", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/884d/7996/1160_normal.png?m=1771515639", "title": "☕Vibe Coding🤖", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/vibecoding", "topics": 224, "footer": "Vibe Coding 适用于快速原型设计和创意探索，但也存在代码理解与安全风险，需要区分“纯粹的”和“负责任的”使用方式。", "header": "Vibe Coding （氛围编程）是一种新兴的软件开发实践，它使用 AI 根据自然语言提示生成代码，加快开发速度，对于编程经验有限的用户尤其如此。\r\n\r\n在这里可以分享所有有关 Vibe Coding 的内容，包括经验、软件、工具、提示词、Agent 、Skill 等。", "title_alternative": "☕Vibe Coding🤖", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/884d/7996/1160_mini.png?m=1771515639", "stars": 315, "founder_id": 51170, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1160, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"id": 593397, "username": "jackOff", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/jackOff", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/40eaa45a823f075189ca2a4f76343678?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/40eaa45a823f075189ca2a4f76343678?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/40eaa45a823f075189ca2a4f76343678?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1662305515, "last_modified": 1662305515, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "CouleurVVEX", "last_touched": 1779962680, "title": "感觉有点 ai 阳痿了，话说你们都用 ai 做了啥", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216088", "created": 1779934899, "deleted": 0, "content": "1-离线翻译插件\r\n2-音乐播放器\r\n3-语音输入法\r\n4-对话生成流程图\r\n5-新闻总结\r\n6-ai 生图、视频、音频\r\n\r\n还有啥有趣的实践吗？", "content_rendered": "<p>1-离线翻译插件\n2-音乐播放器\n3-语音输入法\n4-对话生成流程图\n5-新闻总结\n6-ai 生图、视频、音频</p>\n<p>还有啥有趣的实践吗？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779941853, "replies": 62, "id": 1216088}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/57ae/ee35/229_large.png?m=1448883313", "name": "en", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/57ae/ee35/229_normal.png?m=1448883313", "title": "English", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/en", "topics": 416, "footer": "", "header": "英语学习及使用问题讨论。", "title_alternative": "English", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/57ae/ee35/229_mini.png?m=1448883313", "stars": 395, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 229, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 775417, "username": "NeoWalnut", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/NeoWalnut", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/854e/dae9/775417_mini.png?m=1779853715", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/854e/dae9/775417_normal.png?m=1779853715", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/854e/dae9/775417_large.png?m=1779853715", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/854e/dae9/775417_xlarge.png?m=1779853715", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/854e/dae9/775417_xxlarge.png?m=1779853715", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/854e/dae9/775417_xxxlarge.png?m=1779853715", "created": 1763754764, "last_modified": 1779853715, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "rocklee1108", "last_touched": 1779960393, "title": "英语学了几十年，还是听不懂说不出，大家都是怎么练听说的？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216089", "created": 1779934930, "deleted": 0, "content": "平时工作中偶尔也会用到英语听说，所以一直挺想把英语好好补起来。\r\n\r\n但问题是，英语断断续续学了几十年，感觉还是停留在哑巴英语阶段。看一些简单的英文材料还凑合，但真到听的时候，经常听不全，反应不过来；轮到自己说，又很难组织句子，脑子里一片空白。\r\n\r\n英语 App 试了不少，没有一个有效的，多邻国、流利说、AI 陪练之类的都试过，但整体感觉效果都不太明显。有些是坚持不下去，有些是练完之后感觉没用，还有一些价格也不便宜。\r\n\r\n还上过一些公司的培训课，主要就是老师分享一段材料，然后分组尬聊，感觉这种方式只是在不断强化自己的蹩脚英语，也没啥用。\r\n\r\n大家都是咋练的啊？有啥切实有效的方法么？", "content_rendered": "<p>平时工作中偶尔也会用到英语听说，所以一直挺想把英语好好补起来。</p>\n<p>但问题是，英语断断续续学了几十年，感觉还是停留在哑巴英语阶段。看一些简单的英文材料还凑合，但真到听的时候，经常听不全，反应不过来；轮到自己说，又很难组织句子，脑子里一片空白。</p>\n<p>英语 App 试了不少，没有一个有效的，多邻国、流利说、AI 陪练之类的都试过，但整体感觉效果都不太明显。有些是坚持不下去，有些是练完之后感觉没用，还有一些价格也不便宜。</p>\n<p>还上过一些公司的培训课，主要就是老师分享一段材料，然后分组尬聊，感觉这种方式只是在不断强化自己的蹩脚英语，也没啥用。</p>\n<p>大家都是咋练的啊？有啥切实有效的方法么？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779941730, "replies": 61, "id": 1216089}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_large.png?m=1630643933", "name": "mbp", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_normal.png?m=1630643933", "title": "MacBook Pro", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp", "topics": 9669, "footer": "", "header": "State-of-the-art processors. All-new graphics. Breakthrough high-speed I/O. Three very big leaps forward.", "title_alternative": "MacBook Pro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1630643933", "stars": 3491, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 10, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"id": 700638, "username": "wangyahao2018", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wangyahao2018", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a78/8bc0/700638_mini.png?m=1757502063", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a78/8bc0/700638_normal.png?m=1757502063", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a78/8bc0/700638_large.png?m=1757502063", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a78/8bc0/700638_xlarge.png?m=1757502063", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a78/8bc0/700638_xxlarge.png?m=1757502063", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a78/8bc0/700638_xxxlarge.png?m=1757502063", "created": 1720776457, "last_modified": 1757502063, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "K753255157", "last_touched": 1779963886, "title": "mac 笔记本 500G，开发用，现在没有储存空间了怎么办", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216060", "created": 1779930652, "deleted": 0, "content": "mac 笔记本 500G ，开发用，现在没有储存空间了怎么办\r\n有没有的大佬遇到这样问题的，怎么解决的", "content_rendered": "<p>mac 笔记本 500G ，开发用，现在没有储存空间了怎么办\n有没有的大佬遇到这样问题的，怎么解决的</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779941876, "replies": 59, "id": 1216060}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar